p; The list is maintained in <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://doc=
s.github.com/en/get-started/writing-on-github/getting-started-with-writing-=
and-formatting-on-github/basic-writing-and-formatting-syntax" rel=3D"nofoll=
ow">Git Markdown format</a> so that it can be easily copied into a Devtopia=
 issue for assignment.</p>
