<div class=3D"panelContent" style=3D"background-color: WhiteSmoke;">
<p>[Confluence wiki page can be found here](<a href=3D"https://confluencewi=
kidev.esri.com/display/RTQA/RAT+Output+UDP" rel=3D"nofollow">TCP Client Out=
put</a>)<br>
 ***</p>
<p>Parameters &nbsp;<br>
 - [ ] TCP-client.hostname &nbsp;<br>
 - [ ] TCP-client.port &nbsp;<br>
 - [ ] supportedFormat: delimited &nbsp;<br>
 - [ ] supportedFormat: json &nbsp;<br>
 - [ ] supportedFormat: esri-json &nbsp;<br>
 - [ ] supportedFormat: geo-json<br>
 - [ ] Delimited only: write header row<br>
 - [ ] Delimited only: add delimiter</p>
