<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Verify that ? &nbsp;button links to the correct Help documentation page=
</li>
<li>Verify that there is a Hostname parameter and the Port number are the o=
nly 2 parameters available</li>
<li>Verify that Output data format dropdown options are: GeoJSON, EsriJSON,=
 Delimited, JSON</li>
<li>Verify that if "Delimited" is selected, you have the ability to enable =
headers and set a delimiter. &nbsp;</li>
<li>Verify that you can send data with a hostname (i.e. localhost) or ip ad=
dress (i.e. 127.0.0.1)</li>
<li>Verify that the user receives an error if an invalid port number is pro=
vided</li>
<li>Verifies Delimited and GeoJSON output data formats</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">This is a manual test.&nbsp; This test case is c=
omplete.</td>
